AsianetLoginGui
===============

A python script for logging in to Asianet, and a simple GUI for using it, written in PyQt.

For using the script from command line
--------------------------------------

edit the file asianetloginmain.py and give your username and passord in the __main__ section, then run

$ python asianetloginmain.py

For using the GUI, run
----------------------

$ python asianetlogin.py

